00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:10.320
- It's a good video.

00:02:10.320 --> 00:02:13.610
- [Narrator] Picture if you
will the scene of the crime.

00:02:13.610 --> 00:02:16.820
Nestled on the corner of
Alvarado and Maryland,

00:02:16.820 --> 00:02:20.120
in the posh L.A. neighborhood
of Westlake Park,

00:02:20.120 --> 00:02:24.940
sits the luxurious apartment
of William Desmond Taylor.

00:02:24.940 --> 00:02:27.990
The time: 7:30 a.m.

00:02:27.990 --> 00:02:29.770
February 2nd.

00:02:29.770 --> 00:02:31.910
Taylor's valet, Henry Peavey,

00:02:31.910 --> 00:02:35.778
arrives at his usual time to
make breakfast for Taylor.

00:02:35.778 --> 00:02:38.140
Upon opening the door,

00:02:38.140 --> 00:02:42.910
Peavey spots the obscured feet
of his boss on the ground.

00:02:42.910 --> 00:02:44.930
He calls out to Taylor.

00:02:44.930 --> 00:02:46.400
No response.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:51.170
Creeping in a bit farther,
Peavey discovers to his horror

00:02:51.170 --> 00:02:55.230
the body of William Desmond
Taylor, fully dressed,

00:02:55.230 --> 00:02:58.750
lying face up with blood around his mouth.

00:02:58.750 --> 00:03:01.920
No sign of a struggle
is immediately apparent.

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:05.300
It's assumed he died of natural causes.

00:03:05.300 --> 00:03:07.900
Peavey's shouts alert the neighbors,

00:03:07.900 --> 00:03:11.710
many of them Hollywood stars
and starlets themselves,

00:03:11.710 --> 00:03:14.900
who gradually shuffle
into Taylor's apartment.

00:03:14.900 --> 00:03:15.733
- [Shane] Who's there?

00:03:15.733 --> 00:03:17.810
Like Greta Garbo and Charlie Chaplin?

00:03:17.810 --> 00:03:19.030
"Let's get a load of this bloody man."

00:03:19.030 --> 00:03:19.863
- [Ryan] Well, the thing is,

00:03:19.863 --> 00:03:22.520
