"It was a wild scene."
- It is!

00:03:31.770 --> 00:03:32.730
- The last thing you want

00:03:32.730 --> 00:03:34.780
when there's a crime scene that's fresh

00:03:34.780 --> 00:03:36.902
is everybody shuffling in
their fucking night robes.

00:03:36.902 --> 00:03:38.410
- Walking in with cosmopolitans.

00:03:38.410 --> 00:03:39.243
